author: Robert Kraychik
title: Frank Gaffney: China Lying About Its Coronavirus Status with Media’s Support
description: China is lying about the state of coronavirus within its territory while enjoying support from U.S. news media, said Frank Gaffney.
content:
Frank Gaffney, executive chairman and founder of the Center for Security Policy, said, “We’re not being told the truth by the Chinese Communist Party,” referring to China’s claims regarding the status of the coronavirus outbreak within its borders.
